@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@token =

### ================== USUARIOS (ADMIN) ==================

### Obtener todos los usuarios
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear un usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "usuario.demo",
  "email": "usuario.demo@example.com",
  "password": "Secret123!",
  "status": "ACTIVO",
  "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar.png"
}

###

### Obtener usuario por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar un usuario
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "usuario.actualizado",
  "email": "usuario.demo@example.com",
  "password": "Secret456!",
  "status": "ACTIVO",
  "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar.png"
}

###

### Eliminar un usuario físicamente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Eliminar un usuario lógicamente
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/users/1/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
